{"tid":1672313,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"鄭立: 這種追求怕其他國家「被激嬲」的猜心政治，明明是東方官廷太監的政治","createTime":"2019-10-24T04:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T05:47:19.000Z","uid":1393,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7e516325df981ef50d469f418bca39f9ede48647","tid":1672313,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:38:24.000Z","msg":"當你用外交關係利益，去決定是否支持一件事，意味你認為某國是否支持一個外國的抗爭，不是基於感情與道德或「他們是否有激嬲香港人」，而是出於利害關係的考量。<br />\n<br />\n先不論那根據的權威是否正確，但談到香港時，卻又不談利益關係，轉說別人是否支持香港，是基於感情或道德或被香港人「激嬲」，不是國際關係上的合縱連橫。<br />\n<br />\n這是自相矛盾。所以別會人否支持你，是因為你一些抗爭標語是否有瑞摩上意。<br />\n<br />\n這種追求怕其他國家「被激嬲」的猜心政治，明明是東方官廷太監的政治。<br />\n<br />\n轉載自鄭立Facebook"},{"pid":"8ff6fc408fad449535b20a9a518aaa38568e8e69","tid":1672313,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>SUCK 1026長龍爆買日<br />\n18區爆買日目標黃店（三）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBWe2ef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBWe2ef.png&h=66eab893&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEFLpsB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvEFLpsB.png&h=cdff40ad&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"403a6cccadbed1dc59e9ce41f484d18c6d5dc481","tid":1672313,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c936f149c50f86fc5598c46ec08328a860166a7","tid":1672313,"uid":23672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:40:01.000Z","msg":"又一隻鬼<br />\n叫CC台班軍師情何以堪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841f31a24c3c4b90c87d053249c261e6f8481c2c","tid":1672313,"uid":304845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:42:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d085ff0a71ec1a6f959b19641208d44d5e463d8","tid":1672313,"uid":65074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":